1. You would use LocalDateTime class to store your birthday in years, months, days, seconds, and nanoseconds
2. To find the previous Thursday use TemporalAdjuster.previous(DayofWeek.THURSDAY)
3. ZoneOffset tracks only the absolute offset from UTC.
4. To convert instant to ZonedDateTime use ZonedDateTime.ofInstant method. To convert ZonedDateTime to instant use ZonedDateTime.now().toIstant() from the ChronoZonedDateTime interface.